title: Push Notification Service v1.1.0.0 Release Notes
---


## Changes

- New UI
- Added interactive push support
- Analytics page shows graphs of registered users and pushes over time
- Added ability to search devices
- Added new screen to send push notification with message provided by dashboard user
- Added /healthcheck endpoint that returns of the status of the server and its dependent services.
- Added responsive UI for mobile screens
- Simplified naming (apps, variants and environments are now apps and platforms)
- Cleaned up swagger API documentation for developers
- General UI flow improvements
- Let the /v1/apps endpoint operate on environments and discontinue use of apps.
- API updated to allow fetching all registrations for an application.
- Now shows count of total devices in Devices list
- Improved certificate upload screen for Windows based devices

